source.name: Estimated Schedules for Uranium Enrichment License Applications: AREVA Enrichment Services
source.description: The NRC staff has developed the license review schedule based on the Commission's order to complete the AREVA Enrichment Services Eagle Rock Enrichment Facility license application review within 30 months.
